name: 鏡流 - Jingliu LoRa / Honkai: Star Rail - 崩壊スターレイル
description:
26th Release, 鏡流 - Jingliu From Honkai: Star Rail - 崩壊スターレイル.

Put everything in Filter for seeing all images!

Click on Show more for Weight & Trigger recommendation, Also click on About This Version at Right Corner for more Info.

Warning: It's the Very Very first BETA Version, So It's actually Hard to Use, i will absolutely Update when More Original Art & GameScreencaps are released.

It's was a Challenge + A Request, It's the New Character's from Honkai: Star Rail, it has leaked & I tryed to create a Lora of it with Extremly Low Datasets, i used the same Technique as Sushang & Cocolia Lora, tho this Lora since it's the First version he's Inconsistent with Official Dress.

About this Lora:

  • Lora trained on 44+ Images at the max quality possible. (Atm she's have like 4 Art at Max, I used the same Technique as Sushang & Cocolia Lora).

  • Trained at 512x Resolution.

  • NAI Used, Work with Majority of the Anime Model's.

  • Flexibility is ''Ok''

  • Inconsitent with Official Dress (Not Very Precise), Will be far better when more Art are Released.

For Prompts & Weight:

Flexibility is Ok. (See examples images).

About Trigger Words & Prompts: JingliuV4 (For Trigger) & for prompts just refer to examples images.

Weight recommended: 0.6-0.8. Actually it's work at Weight 1, but i don't recommend for Quality.

Leave a Review & Share you're image in comments if you appreciate this Work :).

modelVersions.name: V4
modelVersions.description:
I pruned White Hair, Red Eyes, so normally you don't need to put in prompt, but if they don't appear put: ((White Hair, Red Eyes)) prompt.

For Official Default Skin: It's hard to get a good precision, Since it's Inconsitent, I recommend to go with 0.7-0.9 Weight.

For Flexibility: for like clothes that don't exist put 0.6 - 0.7 Weight, See my Examples images for this. (Some will work & Other not).

Also if you don't want something to appear, put it in Negative Prompt.
